.6</span> 标题：Schoinos</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：σχοῖνος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：schoinos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc11:5\">2MA 11:5</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>希腊文<em>schoinos</em> 表示的距离等于30斯他迪，约5.6公里（3.5英里）。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc11:5\">2MA 11:5</a> 有一个文本问题，似乎读作“五斯他迪”，但这距离耶路撒冷太近了。在古时，文本就被校订为“五<em>schoinos</em> ”。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
