.7</span> 标题：丈量的杖（measuring rod）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：κάλαμος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：kalamos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:1\">REV 11:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:15\">REV 21:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:16\">REV 21:16</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>和<em>qaneh</em> （参上文）一样，<em>kalamos</em> 也是一种用来丈量的杖。《启示录》没有说明其长度，仅仅给出了被丈量之物的长度。另参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.8.6 丈量的竿、丈量的线（measuring rod, measuring line）&lt;REALIA:1.8.6&gt;</a> 。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
